accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Open for research. Brittle or damaged items are available at the discretion of RAC.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged in two series: Minutes and Reference File. Each series is retained in original order/as received.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This collection contains the Rockefeller Foundation's original finding aids, physical copies of the card catalog index pertaining to Board Minutes and the Reference File maintained by the RF records management staff until the late-1990s.

processinfo.head: Processing Information
processinfo.p: Minimal processing. Records remain in card-file boxes as received.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The index is arranged in original order/as received, with two primary alphabetical runs of cards

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: An alphabetical index by personal name, institutional name, or subject of Board Minutes and associated officer/grant actions. Cards pertaining to grant actions include a summary of the grant, the grant number and the amount awarded. The index also often provides "see also" cross references to associated series/country codes/institutions documented in the Rockefeller Foundation archives.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The index is primarily arranged alphabetically, in original order/as received.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: An alphabetical index by personal name, institutional name, or subject primarily of the Rockefeller Foundations projects/grants, general correspondence, administration program and policy files. The index also often provides "see also" cross references to associated series/country codes/institutions documented in the Rockefeller Foundation archives.
